JO  - The Review of Asset Pricing Studies
JA  - Rev Asset Pric Stud
VL  - 12
IS  - 1
SP  - 336
EP  - 388
SN  - 2045-9920
AB  - We introduce a covariance and spread (i.e., exchange rate forward discount) adjusted carry factor that prices the cross-section of FX market returns, where many other single- and multifactor models fail. Both the covariance matrix of exchange rate growths and forward discounts contain important information for pricing that is not captured by well-known factors. The time-varying conditional covariance matrix and forward discounts forecast future realized currency returns. (JEL F31, F37, G12, G15, G17)
Y2  - 3/26/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1093/rapstu/raab019
ER  - 



